Awesome place. KC is a super welcoming person. She recommended the burger and I'm glad she did. One of the best burgers I've had.  Theo is an amazing cook. Not only that. But he and KC went out of their way to make sure I had what I wanted even if it wasn't on the menu.  I wanted garlic fries. They were not on the menu. But Theo and KC refused to take no for an answer and Theo put together his own little recipe for garlic fries to make sure I had what I wanted  And let me tell you. Theo's garlic fries where some of the best I ever had.  I'm from California and I'm the next time I'm come to Idaho. I expect to see Theo's Garlic fries on the menu.  Super props to KC and Theo going above and beyond to make sure we had what we wanted.

Double Tap Pub was not what I expected. The ambiance was a bit tattered although that's too be expected when trying to keep a social distancing aspect, still could have been swankier. As for the service, it was awesome, two personable, young women serving up wonderfully seasoned entrees and side orders, thank you kitchen, along side nice selections of beer, wine and spirits. Will definitely go back for more recommended favorites from the staff. Good job!
